Creating change takes teamwork, collaboration, and creativity. That is all happening in the campaign to #SafeguardCoastalCarnivores. I'm working with @raincoastconservation and @coastalfirstnations to permanently end commercial trophy hunting of all large carnivores on the coast of British Columbia, like this beautiful and inquisitive coastal wolf.

@aprilbencze, @tavishcampbell, @karencooperphoto, @colleengaraphoto, @bertiegregory, @melissagroo, @johnmarriot @neileverosborne, @eric_sambol_photography, Andrew S. Wright, Brad Hill and myself are donating prints of the carnivores at risk to raise funds to help protect them. This is mine. These fine art prints will be auctioned at each exhibit: @karencooperphoto gallery in Vancouver, @batemancentre in Victoria, @audainartmuseum in Whistler.
See the link in my bio for more information and to bid.
